data.description: Totally renovated gorgeous all brick ranch home located on 2+ acres of land. This beautifully remodeled home features 4 bedrooms and 2 baths along with an open concept living, kitchen, and dining room. Some of the upgrades include plumbing, electrical, roof, HVAC, flooring, carpet, tile, granite counter tops in kitchen and bathrooms, tile showers, recessed lighting throughout home, security system, Bluetooth light/fan combo in master bathroom, his and her closets in oversized master bedroom, brand new led motion detector lights outside of home, workshop with electricity. New Stainless steel appliances. New patio with firepit in place and huge back covered porch. There are 2 drive ways for this home with a circular drive and room for RV parking and/or tractor trailer parking. There are blueberry that have recently been planted on property. Home is semi private with only one other home on this road! There is so much to enjoy about this home from the peace and tranquility to walking distance to the Silver Comet Trail (property is adjacent to this trail) and Chief Ladiga Trail. 2.2 miles to the Highland Motorcycle Park and 3.5 miles to the Indian Mountain ATV park. Don't miss out on your opportunity to see this magnificent home today!
